==English==
===Etymology===
Named after its [[inventor]], Richard Gatling.

===Noun===
'''gatling gun'''
# A type of [[machine gun]] with several [[barrel]]s on a [[rotating]] frame, still used today on some modern [[aircraft]] and [[naval]] weapons.

